In the honor system established by the {{ill|Joi Jōrei|ja|叙位条例|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Joi Jōrei|qq=}} (Imperial Edict No. 10 of 1887) and the {{ill|Ikai-ryō|ja|位階令|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ikai-ryō|qq=}} (Imperial Edict No. 325 of 1926), no Rank corresponding to 九位 (Kyū-i) was included.

